snippet.title: Smashy Duo v2 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Smashy Duo is an unique fast-paced arcade action game where you control 2 Heroes to hit as many monsters before one of them was knocked off from the stage.

https://goo.gl/yQPg7z
